{"id":839125025,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1 year, 7 months","timestamp":1667878381,"status":11,"status_display":"Wrong Answer","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/839125025/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"N/A","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        HashMap<Character, Integer> map=  new HashMap<>();\n        \n        \n        int st =0, max=0;\n        \n        boolean con = false;\n        \n        for(int i=0; i<s.length(); i++){\n            if(!map.containsKey(s.charAt(i))){\n                map.put(s.charAt(i), i);\n            }else{\n                con = true;\n                max = Math.max(max, i-map.get(s.charAt(i)));\n                st = map.get(s.charAt(i))+1;\n                map.put(s.charAt(i), i);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        if(con==false)\n            return s.length();\n        \n        max= Math.max(max, s.length()-st);\n        return max;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
